msgstr "# triton.language.sum"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/sum.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/sum.md:4
msgid "简介：`triton.language.sum` 计算输入tensor沿指定轴的元素和，返回求和结果。"
msgstr "Introduction: `triton.language.sum` computes the sum of elements of the input tensor along the specified axis and returns the summation result."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/sum.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.sum(input, axis=None, keep_dims=False)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/sum.md:8
msgid ""
"> **版本差异说明**\n"
">\n"
"> `dtype` 参数为社区 Triton 3.5.0 引入的功能。当前发布的 Triton-Ascend 基于社区 Triton 3.2.0 开发，没有`dtype` 参数。后续升级至社区 Triton 3.5.0 版本时，将完整支持 `dtype` 参数的功能。\n"
msgstr ""
"> **Version Difference Note**\n"
">\n"
"> The `dtype` parameter is a feature introduced in community Triton 3.5.0. The currently released Triton-Ascend is developed based on community Triton 3.2.0 and does not have the `dtype` parameter. When upgrading to community Triton 3.5.0 in the future, full support for the `dtype` parameter will be provided.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/sum.md:10
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/sum.md:12
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/sum.md:14
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | 输入tensor |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` 或 `None` | 沿着哪个维度进行求和操作。如果为None，则对所有维度求和 |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | 如果为True，保持被求和的维度为长度1 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"|----------------|------|-------------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | Input tensor |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` or `None` | The dimension along which to perform the sum operation. If None, sum over all dimensions |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | If True, keep the summed dimensions as length 1 |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/sum.md:16
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：计算输入tensor沿指定轴的元素和，返回求和结果。\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: Computes the sum of elements of the input tensor along the specified axis, and returns the summation result.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/sum.md:18
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

